        "TileImage": "$($repository 68117bbe-9908-4676-856c-ba4529c95f30).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47. Your target is Somboon Murang, a rather troublesome staff member working in the Himmapan Hotel in Bangkok.\r\rShe is responsible for the compromised status of various missions in the area. Murang is known by the agency as &quot;The Bane of Unseen Falls&quot;, a nickname given to her after witnessing a number of agents dump people off of railings.\r\rOur client, a disgruntled ICA agent who is tired of her antics, has asked us to ensure she doesn&apos;t fuck with us again.\r\rGood luck, 47.",
